{"tid":2272146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"員工寧被裁：簽新約如受罰","createTime":"2020-11-05T02:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T10:48:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac5670446fca91c0cfc77b065ddd477ca9cbc55","tid":2272146,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/OD44GDUVU5APXJNMBKSIQB3G4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FOD44GDUVU5APXJNMBKSIQB3G4Q%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4PvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=e76c0b3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FOD44GDUVU5APXJNMBKSIQB3G4Q%2F&h=81f5c5e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/OD44GDUVU5APXJNMBKSIQB3G4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n員工寧被裁：簽新約如受罰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5pR-x0ABCa40VlfP92xhj6SuxP4=/1805x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HIAQ7GVXJBAO3IN5KDQ454CQ5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5pR-x0ABCa40VlfP92xhj6SuxP4%3D%2F1805x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHIAQ7GVXJBAO3IN5KDQ454CQ5U.jpg&h=1c104f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國泰資方代表避見員工和傳媒，會議結束後在保鑣護航下衝入大樓電梯。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今日凌晨是國泰倖存員工續約死線。有員工透露，難以接受新合約下薪酬被大幅度降低，不打算簽新約，「寧願畀人裁好過要簽份新約，好似懲罰緊留低嘅人」；亦有員工因經濟原因決定簽新約，「講真個package人工方面係生活唔到，拎住個底薪叫過渡下」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國泰企硬 拒押後簽辣約期限<br />\n<br />\n任職國泰空姐六年的F小姐（化名）表示不打算簽新合約，「𠵱家時薪177蚊，新約時薪減到155蚊，底薪由1.2萬減到一萬元，都諗咗幾日，但接受唔到人工咁減」。<br />\n<br />\n她估計，不簽新約被。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nJ先生（化名）任國泰空少五年半，。。。。。。。。。。。。。在新約下，他的時薪由170元降至155元，每月底薪僅萬多元。由於開工不足，他現正兼職客戶服務以維持生計，亦會繼續搵工，隨時逃離「惡晒」社團。"},{"pid":"f71f3ca68020b935a78963565eada65c0b74afca","tid":2272146,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"21ea0cb18e5a5d45257e00ea6b6696c558bf05c3","tid":2272146,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"根本突登 等你自己合理化被裁"},{"pid":"29707ad328618c0358f8198686e4c7be2e4162fa","tid":2272146,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"時薪有150都幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85394e74f14f363f4c1541926ab4d420a144854","tid":2272146,"uid":7444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29707ad328618c0358f8198686e4c7be2e4162fa","tid":2272146,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"時薪有150都幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"你估下 一個月要返幾多個鐘?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755bbc726ee4981f8bfef38be99ebbcd5226591b","tid":2272146,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85394e74f14f363f4c1541926ab4d420a144854","tid":2272146,"uid":7444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29707ad328618c0358f8198686e4c7be2e4162fa","tid":2272146,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"時薪有150都幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"你估下 一個月要返幾多個鐘?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"我點估<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c086d1b50b44646da5d3c5be1afbbd0bf1355639","tid":2272146,"uid":